Bartleby-Big plump and fat banana
Sonia-Sweet strawberry donuts
Manic-Delicious fresh salad with finely chopped carrots, walnuts and ranch dressing. 
Sonic-Sweet and warm blueberry tea
Knuckles-Red sprinkles
Mindy-A juicy orange
